Changed release date back to March 8, 1994, as nearly all online sources other than Google Play list the release date as March 8. February 19, 1994 was a Saturday, and nearly all albums in the U.S. were being released on Tuesdays in 1994. The album debuted at #1 on the Billboard 200 in the issue dated March 26, 1994. Had the album been released on February 19, it would have been #1 in the issue dated March 12.
